{"tid":1985917,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★【油價見負】點止「原油寶」！傳相關QDII基金虧損達7成","createTime":"2020-04-23T13:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T00:17:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"70741d4457dda54176431de1bd83f54614ee11fe","tid":1985917,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:07:39.000Z","msg":"國際油價一度跌至「負值」，使到內地投資者在「紙石油」上招致巨額損失！然而，影響不止如此，據報內地的原油類QDII基金最多虧損達7成。<br />\n<br />\n所謂的合格境內機構投資者(QDII)基金，是指境內設立投資境外證券市場的一種證券投資基金，即是它是以國內資金投資海外巿場。今年投資油氣的QDII基金，累計跌幅基本都超過3成。<br />\n統計顯示，目前市場中共有7只油氣類QDII基金，分別是華寶油氣、南方原油、易方達原油、廣發石油、嘉實原油、諾安油氣、廣發道瓊斯石油指數基金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200423/bkn-20200423203434857-0423_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200423%2Fbkn-20200423203434857-0423_00842_001.html&d=7FLALsszV4LuAMmN05fc6hksnaRIvLJvZlYWuj0OsWg%3D&h=d51de3d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200423/bkn-20200423203434857-0423_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"0cbdc9460bab5f47f8ab95bddb3c7aef87a5a378","tid":1985917,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-23T13:07:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0623f27cafc3e7c488bc05732730fb846e5ca7c","tid":1985917,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T00:17:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}